{"id": 2819, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都有哪些“多任务强迫症”？", "description": "吃饭的时候如果没有剧看，就觉得连饭都吃不下去。（题图来自：iStock ️©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 19485, "comment_count": 46, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190304190252tjrUDI9aCK0fcEm5.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-04T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5461, "title": "现如今你都有哪些“多任务强迫症”？", "content": "现如今你都有哪些“多任务强迫症”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 330752, "content": "洗澡/刷牙的同时，在脑子里思考工作/人生问题", "image": "img/option/option/20190304202116j52d7UgcPYkBzF0n.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330753, "content": "等待网页加载的时候，抓紧时间再开另一个网页", "image": "img/option/option/2019030420182334K5xyCIAqXPibg1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330755, "content": "吃饭的时候，一定要挑一部下饭剧来看", "image": "img/option/option/20190304201649dKcvDneHhrb7GpkM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330757, "content": "等泡面的几分钟，收拾桌上的文具杂物", "image": "img/option/option/20190304201518QebqwsFpKiVPItH1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330771, "content": "排队/坐地铁/等车，还可以见缝插针回几封邮件", "image": "img/option/option/20190304201308i5Kvx1ta9Owybnre.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330782, "content": "看视频的时候，会顺便留心弹幕里有啥好玩的梗", "image": "img/option/option/20190304201156J24PUSAXnCkaqGrV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330746, "content": "微信聊天的时候，一定要顺便刷几篇公众号文章", "image": "img/option/option/20190304200939IOpQCALUWvFr2gMD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330751, "content": "干家务的时候，一定要打开电视或者听听歌", "image": "img/option/option/20190304202321QH8yut143Dj2VmMb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 330783, "content": "都不会，我是单项任务专员，一次只能做一件事", "image": "img/option/option/20190304202406JSsH12PFmzvoDeKT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}